      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$19,900 - Honest fair-condition driver that offers a good entry point for someone looking for an enjoyable car without paying top-dollar. It shows its age and use in places, but it still presents decently overall, runs and drives, and has the kind of solid potential that makes it appealing for a hands-on owner or someone who values affordability over perfection. A straightforward car with some flaws, priced accordingly.",
