    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition car that presents nicely overall and should make a solid buy for someone wanting a clean, honest vehicle. The exterior and interior show normal light wear consistent with age and use, but nothing that takes away from it being a respectable, good driver. Not a mint showpiece, but a strong example that has clearly been maintained better than average and should meet the expectations of a buyer looking for a dependable, nice-presenting car.",
