      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for someone seeking affordable transportation at a great value. It shows its age and would benefit from some attention, but it remains a straightforward option for a buyer who appreciates honest used-car pricing and solid potential. A smart pick for a commuter, project, or spare vehicle.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t a showpiece, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It\u2019s priced to make sense, and if you\u2019re after honest value rather than something flashy, this could be a great fit. A friendly, no-pressure sale from someone who just wants to match it with the right next owner.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with solid bones and plenty of usable life left for the right buyer. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels like a strong foundation for a dependable budget commuter, shop truck, or straightforward project. Cosmetically it shows age and use, but that also means no mystery about what you\u2019re getting\u2014just a mechanically serviceable vehicle with practical value. If you want an affordable car with character, good core components, and room to improve as you go, this one makes a compelling entry point.",
      "price": 8450.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap entry point. Runs, drives, and gets the job done. Not pretty. Perfect project, work car, or parts donor. Priced to move.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with stories in its steel and plenty of road still left for the right driver. It has that honest, lived-in character enthusiasts recognize immediately\u2014an ideal canvas for a budget commuter, weekend project, or dependable runabout for someone who values utility over flash. There\u2019s a certain charm in a vehicle that\u2019s ready to be put to work, and this one offers exactly that: straightforward purpose, strong personality, and an entry point that makes sense. If you\u2019ve been looking for affordable wheels with grit, presence, and potential, this is the kind of find that deserves a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable, honest-value vehicle priced for the buyer who wants low upfront cost and solid potential. This car is best suited for someone seeking a budget-friendly project, backup transportation, or a practical option with room to make it their own. A straightforward opportunity to get into a vehicle at an accessible price.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    }
